# Invite links: /join/<game-id> open the app on a device that has Jottly (via the
# apple-app-site-association file); on everything else they fall through to this landing page.
# Target the extensionless /invite (not /invite.html) so Cloudflare's automatic .html stripping
# can't bounce the rewrite through a 307 - this serves the page in place at the original URL.
/join/*  /invite  200
/join    /invite  200
